{"type": "article", "id": 15081, "title": "吹风扇的灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-18T07:26:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153148nuBrpoLEZzh8XVtj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t法国设计师 Marc Venot 带来了两盏灯，来诠释膨胀和收缩的过程。其中一盏灯罩采用手工缝制拼接的聚乙烯泡沫，里面安装了一个塑料做的小风扇。启动时，空气通过风扇填充进了灯罩里面，使灯罩像热气球一样升到一定高度，并微微摇晃。不用的时候灯罩又落在灯泡上。而另一盏灯的灯罩有无数长条孔，在风扇的吹动下也有动感。<a href=\"http://www.marc-venot.com/Lumiere-soufflee\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142413qZsFUdI9DEXLpmb3.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142413D97g2nVuHvhN0Msk.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"619\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75672372\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142414P0pcnULdaBiW9SJ2.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"575\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70293399\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142414TpQKPXtAMJbLB0FU.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"613\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142415A9ho3c2nbuig4xMy.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"613\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}